%N A145882 Triangle read by rows: T(n,k) is the number of even permutations of {1,2,...,n} having k descents (n >= 1, k >= 0).
%C A145882 Number of entries in row n is 1+floor(binomial(n,2)/2)-floor(binomial(n-2,2)/2).
